# `shadcn build` output. Treating these as build artifacts (regenerated on
# every `pnpm registry:build` / Vercel deploy) so palette edits in
# `registry.json` can never silently ship the previous build's `theme.json`.
public/r/

# Incremental-build manifests written by scripts/generate-{props,a11y,tests}.ts.
# Regenerated on every `pnpm generate:*` run; tracking them creates churn.
